    <numbered_3_para>the Contractor has the right to perform and/or provide the Services and fulfil zir obligations under this Contract from any place and at such times as the Contractor shall determine at zir own discretion;</numbered_3_para>
    <numbered_3_para>the Contractor shall bear all taxes on zir earnings as required by Applicable Law, and shall be solely and fully responsible for the calculation and prompt payment of any applicable taxes to the home and host tax authorities as determined by zir local taxation legislation, and the Company bears no tax liabilities for the Contractor nor shall the Company pay any taxes (including any withholding taxes) for Contractor; and</numbered_3_para>
    <numbered_3_para>the Contractor has no entitlements to any overtime pay, vacation pay, sick leave, retirement benefits, social security, employee compensation, health or disability benefits, unemployment insurance benefits, or employee benefits of any kind.</numbered_3_para>

